      the Service, you agree to these terms. If you are using the Service for an organisation, you
      confirm you are authorised to bind it, and "you" means that organisation.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Who these terms are with</h2>
    <p>
      The Service is provided by <strong>{ENTITY}</strong>, registry code 17517227, Sepapaja tn 6,
      15551 Tallinn, Harju Maakond, Estonia ("we", "us", "mitos"). You can reach us at
